            </h2>
            <p class="text-[17px] text-gray-700 md:text-lg font-roboto">
                Ramadan 2024 is a sacred time for Muslims worldwide, marked by fasting, prayer, and acts of charity. It's a month where individuals come together to deepen their connection with Allah, seeking forgiveness and guidance. From dawn till sunset, believers abstain from food and drink, focusing instead on spiritual nourishment. It's a time of self-discipline, empathy for the less fortunate, and community unity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-5 row-gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div
              class="bg-white border-l-4 border-green-500 shadow-sm border-deep-purple-accent-400"
            >
              <div class="h-full p-5 border border-l-0 rounded-r">
                <p class="text-sm
                 text-gray-900 font-roboto">
                 "Ramadan: Month of fasting and prayer for Muslims. Focus on spiritual growth, reflection, and community unity."
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="bg-white border-l-4 border-green-500 shadow-sm border-deep-purple-accent-400"
            >
              <div class="h-full p-5 border border-l-0 rounded-r">
                <p class="text-sm font-roboto text-gray-900 ">
                    "During Ramadan, Muslims fast from dawn to sunset, break fast with iftar, and engage in increased charity."
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="text-center">
            <a
              href="https://edhi-donate.tscube.co.in/"
