          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-20">
          <img
            class="object-cover w-full h-100 rounded shadow-lg sm:h-30rem mt-6"
            src="/images/ramadan-1.jpg"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <br /><br />
  <Donationcard programId={[1, 4, 13, 17]} />

  <!-- providings ended here -->
  <!-- section-1 area started -->
  <section class="text-center px-8">
    <h1 class="text-green-700 text-4xl font-bold">
        Extend a Helping Hand this Ramadan    </h1>
    <br />
    <div class="sm:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <p class="text-[17px] font-roboto">
            Extend Your Support to Those in Need this Ramadan and Make a Lasting Impact.
        </p><br />
        <div class="border-b-8 border-red-600 w-64 mx-auto my-2 rounded-md">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row pt-4">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 border-r-4 border-green-500 pr-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify text-[17px] font-roboto">
            This Ramadan, Muslims around the world eagerly wait for it each year. It's avery important time focusing on devotion, mercy, and getting closer to Allah(swt). It's a chance for us to ask for forgiveness sincerely, think about ourblessings, and help those who are in need. It's a time to realize how lucky weare and to understand the difficulties faced by people in poor communities likeSyria, Pakistan, Palestine, Yemen, and the Gambia. <br><br>You can support our Ramadan Appeal by giving your Zakat to those who need itthe most. During Ramadan, many of us choose not to eat during daylight hours.But for many people worldwide, hunger is a daily reality. Millions don't havefood for iftar and continue to suffer from hunger. The COVID-19 pandemic hasmade this situation worse, leaving millions more without enough food. Around795 million people go hungry every day, not knowing when they'll eat next. Manyare malnourished, lacking the right nutrients to survive.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pl-4">
          <h5 class="text-green-700 font-bold text-justify pb-2">
            The Prophet (saw) said that “Whoever observes fasts during the month of Ramadan out of sincere faith, and hoping to attain Allah’s rewards, then all his past sins will be forgiven.” [Bukhari]
          </h5>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify text-[17px] font-roboto">
            This Ramadan, consider donating your Zakat to our Ramadan Appeal. Zakat is aduty for every adult, sane Muslim who owns wealth above a certain value. Yougive 2.5% of your wealth to those in need. Your Zakat can save lives, providenecessities like clean water, food, shelter, education, and healthcare, andhelp families escape poverty. <br><br>In Ramadan, good deeds are greatly rewarded All acts of kindness areincreased seventyfold by Allah (swt). So, your donations during Ramadan canmake a big impact, helping entire communities rise out of poverty and providinglong-term solutions to hunger and poverty.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- section-1 area ended -->

  <br /><br /><br /><br /><br />
  <!-- section-2 area started -->

  <section>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold flex justify-center">
        Embrace the Blessings of &nbsp; <span class="text-green-700"> Ramadan</span>
    </h1>
    <br />

    <div class="text-center pb-6 mb-4">
      <p class="text-[17px] font-roboto">
        Ramadan is a holy month observed by Muslims worldwide, marked by fasting, prayer, reflection, and acts of charity, fostering spiritual growth and community unity.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 pb-4 pt-6 ">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 pl-4 pr-4 mb-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 w-full h-60 shadow-lg transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400">
            <h6>Fasting and<span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Reflection</span></h6><br />
            <p class="font-roboto">Muslims abstain from food and drink from dawn till sunset, focusing on spiritual nourishment and self-reflection, cultivating discipline and mindfulness in their daily lives.
            </p>
            <a href="" class="transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400"></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 pl-4 pr-4 mb-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 w-full h-60 shadow-lg transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400">
            <h6>Prayer and <span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Devotion</span></h6><br />
            <p class="font-roboto">Increased prayers and recitation of the Quran deepen spiritual connections with Allah (swt) during Ramadan, providing moments of solace and guidance in challenging times.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 pl-4 pr-4 mb-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 w-full h-60 shadow-lg transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400">
            <h6>Acts of<span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Charity</span></h6><br />
            <p class="font-roboto">Ramadan emphasizes generosity, encouraging Muslims to give to those in need through Zakat and Sadaqah, embodying the principles of compassion and empathy towards others.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 pl-4 pr-4 mb-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 w-full h-60 shadow-lg transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400">
            <h6>Community <span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Unity</span></h6><br />
            <p class="font-roboto">Muslims come together for iftar, breaking fast as a community, fostering unity and solidarity, creating bonds that transcend differences and strengthen the fabric of society.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 pl-4 pr-4 mb-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 w-full h-60 shadow-lg transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400">
            <h6>Family  <span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Bonding</span></h6><br />
            <p class="font-roboto">Ramadan strengthens family ties through shared meals, prayers, and spiritual activities, nurturing a sense of belonging and support within the household.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 pl-4 pr-4 mb-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-300 p-4 w-full h-60 shadow-lg transition hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-green-400">
            <h6>Gratitude and<span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Forgiveness</span></h6><br />
            <p class="font-roboto">Muslims seek forgiveness, reflect on blessings, and express gratitude for Allah's mercy and blessings during Ramadan, fostering a profound sense of humility and appreciation for the blessings bestowed upon them.</p>

          </div>
        </div>
      
      </div>
    </div>
    

    <!-- content area ended -->
  </section><br /><br /><br />

  <!-- section-2 area ended -->
  <!-- section 2.1 started -->
  <section>
    <div
      class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto sm:max-w-xl md:max-w-full lg:max-w-screen-xl md:px-24 lg:px-8 lg:py-20"
    >
      <div class="grid gap-5 row-gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="max-w-xl mb-6">
            <h2
              class="max-w-lg  font-sans text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl sm:leading-none"
            >
            Fulfilling Your Zakat Obligation in<span class="text-green-600">&nbsp;Ramadan</span>              <br class="hidden md:block" />
              <span class="relative px-1">
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-3 transform -skew-x-12 bg-teal-accent-400"
                >
                </div>
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-[17px] text-gray-700 md:text-lg font-roboto">
                Ramadan is an opportune time for Muslims to fulfill their Zakat obligation. Zakat, a pillar of Islam, involves giving a portion of one's wealth to those in need. <br><br>During Ramadan, the blessings of charity are multiplied, making it an ideal time to support the less fortunate and uplift communities. By giving Zakat, Muslims not only fulfill a religious duty but also contribute to the betterment of society, spreading compassion and kindness.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-5 row-gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div
              class="bg-white border-l-4 border-green-500 shadow-sm border-deep-purple-accent-400"
            >
              
            </div>
            
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="text-center">
            <a
              href="https://edhi-donate.tscube.co.in/"
              class="flex justify-center items-center h-12 px-6 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white border border-green-500"
            >
              Donate Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-[400px]">
          <img
            class="object-cover w-full h-100 rounded shadow-lg sm:h-30rem mt-6"
            src="/images/ramadan-2.jpg"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <!-- section 2.1 ended -->


  <!-- section-3 area started -->
 <section class="py-">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-10 md:px-12 lg:px-5 space-y-16">
