              Highlighting our milestones and accomplishments, showcasing the positive impact of our efforts in <br> serving humanity and fostering hope.
            </p><br />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-10 pb-12">
            <div class="relative aspect-[5/3.8] rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/awards-main.jpg" alt="project cover" width="1300" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-800 dark:from-gray-900 flex flex-col justify-end p-5 space-y-5 text-gray-300">
                    <h1 class="font-semibold text-white text-2xl">
Zakat Calculator                    </h1>
